Jhasan's decision:

Under this Government Decision, administrative sanction is being granted to BYG Government Medical College & Sassoon General Hospital, Pune under the Department for purchase of Turnkey Machinery & Equipment worth Rs. 46,50,00, 000 / - (Rupees forty six crores, fifty lakhs only) (including all taxes) required for patient care in the Department of Gynaecology & Obstetrics in the Institute from the grants sanctioned under the State Plan during the financial year 2024-25 subject to the following conditions.
Conditions: - 1) This administrative approval 2024-25 is being made from the funds available from the provision sanctioned under the State Plan in this financial year.
